Package: text.analyzer
Title: Text Analyzer Tool for R 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Yusra", "Kunduzi", , "yusra.kunduzi@student.hu.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of 4 functions for quick text analysis in R. 
    The 'text_summary' tool analyzes the text and summarizes the word count, 
    sentence count, and average word length. 
    The 'longest_word' function gives you the longest word and its position in the text. 
    The 'top10_words' function counts the 10 words that are most frequent in the text. 
    The 'sentence_summary' function summarizes the total number of sentences, 
    the average wordcount per sentence, the longest sentence, the shortest sentence and a readability score.
